story:
In the quiet library, Sarah glimpsed
Through a keyhole, a shadow shifted.
Sarah's trying to decide whether should she Follow by she has no clue of what that thing is so she decided to stay still
Presley Sarah just saw a shadow but then light came by and see she saw a man with the mascot on

"Oddly, he held a puzzle piece,
Whence did it come? increased her unease."
Sarah knows that puzzle may lead to a surprise so she asked her if he needs her help solving this puzzle
Sarah had a friend with her and he and she tried to get support from her friend

"Danger lurks," her friend surmised,
"Hold tight, for the puzzle is disguised."
Sarah decides to follow her friends and she stay still in the library anyway
so they decided to follow the Shadow and after that they discovered that a thief has entered into the library and they tried to catch him
